 with the requirements for publication in two EasyChair series: the EPiC Series and Kalpa Publications [CITATION Vor04 \l 1033 ]. EasyChair is a conference management system that is flexible, easy to use, and has many features to make it suitable for various conference models. It is currently probably the most commonly used conference management system [ CITATION Vor04 \l 1033 ], serving thousands of conferences every year.</w:t></w:r></w:p><w:sectPr><w:type w:val="nextPage"/><w:pgSz w:w="11906" w:h="16838"/><w:pgMar w:left="1134" w:right="1134" w:header="0" w:top="1134" w:footer="0" w:bottom="1134" w:gutter="0"/><w:pgNumType w:fmt="decimal"/><w:formProt w:val="false"/><w:textDirection w:val="lrTb"/><w:docGrid w:type="default" w:linePitch="240" w:charSpace="4294961151"/></w:sectPr></w:body></w:document>